  <p>
    Insurance costs for Zimbabwe (USD widely used):
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

  <h3>Cost-Saving Strategies</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Harare base:</strong> Best local healthcare</li>
    <li><strong>South Africa network:</strong> Use designated hospitals</li>
    <li><strong>High deductible:</strong> Local care affordable in USD</li>
    <li><strong>Regional plans:</strong> Southern Africa focused</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="scenarios">Real-World Scenarios</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 1: Victoria Falls Tourism, 67</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $3,000/month income. Business permit. Vic Falls.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Cigna Global with Johannesburg evacuation.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$550/month. Tourism lifestyle; South Africa backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 2: Returning Zimbabwean, 71</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $2,500/month UK pension. Returning home. Harare.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> BUPA Global with UK and South Africa coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$700/month. Home return; comprehensive backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 3: Conservation Worker, 66</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $2,000/month income. Residence permit. Hwange area.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Cigna Global with strong evacuation coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$520/month. Remote location; comprehensive backup.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Common Questions</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is Zimbabwe safe?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Generally safe—lower violent crime than South Africa. Political situation requires monitoring. Tourist areas secure. Normal urban precautions in cities. Wildlife areas very safe. Overall safer than reputation suggests.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What about the economy/currency?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        USD widely used—most transactions in dollars. Local currency exists but USD dominant. Bring USD cash. ATMs work but have limits. Credit cards increasingly accepted. Economic situation improving but remains complex.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is English sufficient?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Yes—English is official language. Business, government, healthcare all in English. High literacy rate. Educated population. British colonial heritage. No language barrier for English speakers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What's Victoria Falls like?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Spectacular—one of world's great natural wonders. Tourism town with restaurants, hotels, activities. Good infrastructure for tourists. Helicopter, bungee, rafting available. Zimbabwe side often considered better view than Zambia side.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Ready to Compare Options?</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Get quotes from providers for Zimbabwe coverage.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/allianz-care" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Allianz Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-0">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide is for informational purposes only. Insurance requirements, visa regulations, and healthcare access rules change regularly. Always verify current requirements with Zimbabwe authorities and consult with a licensed insurance professional.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
